    {
      "id": "PopularPost317857",
      "post_content": "This is fantastic in Commander, where people play cards like [Blightsteel Colossus](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Blightsteel Colossus) and [Hamletback Goliath](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hamletback Goliath) all the time. The instant speed and tapping effect mean that it stops that creature from attacking you the turn they cast it. I guess I could characterize it as a [Fend Off](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fend Off) stapled to an [Act of Treason](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Act of Treason), which seems like value. I play this in my Darigaaz EDH deck for the flavor, but also because it is really good. 4.5/5  \n  \nSee also: [Delirium](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Delirium)",
      "posted_by": "Aremath",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost317857\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">This is fantastic in Commander, where people play cards like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Blightsteel Colossus\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Blightsteel Colossus\">Blightsteel Colossus</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Hamletback Goliath\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hamletback Goliath\">Hamletback Goliath</a> all the time. The instant speed and tapping effect mean that it stops that creature from attacking you the turn they cast it. I guess I could characterize it as a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Fend Off\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fend Off\">Fend Off</a> stapled to an <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Act of Treason\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Act of Treason\">Act of Treason</a>, which seems like value. I play this in my Darigaaz EDH deck for the flavor, but also because it is really good. 4.5/5<br/><br/>See also: <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Delirium\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Delirium\">Delirium</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '317857'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy97652\">Aremath</span>\r\n                                (5/